Class AbstractEmbosser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.daisy.dotify.api.factory.AbstractFactory
      • org.daisy.braille.utils.impl.tools.embosser.AbstractEmbosser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, org.daisy.dotify.api.embosser.Embosser, org.daisy.dotify.api.embosser.EmbosserFactoryProperties, org.daisy.dotify.api.embosser.EmbosserProperties, org.daisy.dotify.api.factory.Factory, org.daisy.dotify.api.factory.FactoryProperties

    BrailloEmbosser, CidatEmbosser, EnablingTechnologiesEmbosser, GenericEmbosser, IndexEmbosser, Interpoint55Embosser, MountbattenEmbosser, TigerEmbosser

    public abstract class AbstractEmbosser
extends org.daisy.dotify.api.factory.AbstractFactory
implements org.daisy.dotify.api.embosser.Embosser
    Provides an abstract base for Embossers, implementing basic features such as the ability to set page format, table, and cell height and width.
